{"tid":804192,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌拿星 呀媽早餐比杯熱水我 搞到我返學遲到...","createTime":"2018-09-02T23:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T08:56:16.000Z","uid":1734,"like":23,"dislike":249,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"5e7db9d3ef9000141d97654bcb6bfa586f47d3c4","tid":804192,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T23:50:14.000Z","msg":"岩岩食早餐，阿媽唔知做乜比杯熱水我<br />\n算la,我照飲，真係頂唔順<br />\n跟住加左d溫水<br />\n我呀媽猛係度話我渣渣渣<br />\n對話:<br />\n仆:渣ga<br />\n我:咁我唔飲得熱a ma<br />\n隔左一陣<br />\n仆:乜咁渣ga<br />\n我: ----&gt;忍緊<br />\n仆:惺咁渣ga<br />\n我:屌,我係飲唔到ga,la洗唔洗嗌我渣a(好大聲咁講)<br />\n跟住佢惡過我<br />\n仲想打我,屌<br />\n我韾韾地<br />\n返入房打呢編野<br />\n過左一陣,我家姐同我講+凍水比我繼續飲<br />\n我話唔要,<br />\n之後條仆街又嘈<br />\n仆:由得佢la,岩岩咁大聲同我講野,想聲巴佢<br />\n家姐幫口話講笑<br />\n我又忍唔9住<br />\n我:你講笑就得,我講笑你就韾<br />\n跟住佢又話,你真係以為唔驚我打你,依家你係老母定我係老母<br />\n我又同佢講,你咪a你,我報警tim a<br />\n跟住佢冇出聲<br />\n痴線 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後嬲到早餐都無食去左返學 以家遲左好多出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一日就遲到  唉...  比老母累死"},{"pid":"875c534d32fc7e06bda3eb71393fc1ac817d3b3b","tid":804192,"uid":555,"like":160,"dislike":1,"score":159,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T23:52:51.000Z","msg":"好撚低汁 快啲躝啦"},{"pid":"e552be7918349a5b210006c1f9af3a06d4370852","tid":804192,"uid":113807,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T23:54:30.000Z","msg":"睇完依篇文 搞到我返工遲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f481713a637d71fe7234f812c9e0533d6601e5","tid":804192,"uid":151675,"like":5,"dislike":24,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T23:55:02.000Z","msg":"尷尬到睇唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主加油"},{"pid":"2cca66fb833102eb782460864d601b30c3dcb713","tid":804192,"uid":1734,"like":13,"dislike":16,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"